class="block-intro-text"><p>A cleaning business provides cleaning and maintenance services for residential and commercial buildings, construction sites, and more. The benefits of starting a cleaning business include low overhead costs, the absence of typical operating costs, and high customer demand. Follow our guide below to help you to start and grow your cleaning business.</p></div></div></div></div><div
