class="block block-pros-cons"><h2 id=pros-and-cons>Pros and Cons:</h2><div
class="row pros-cons-wrapper"><div
class="col-md-6"><div
class="pros-cons pros"><div
class="heading">Pros</div><ul
class="list list-unstyled"><li>Low startup and overhead costs.</li><li>You only need basic cleaning experience to start a business.</li><li>Flexible work schedule.</li><li>Good growth potential.</li><li>Minimal paperwork.</li><li>Depending on your state, you don&#039;t need a business license.</li></ul></div></div><div
class="col-md-6"><div
class="pros-cons cons"><div
class="heading">Cons</div><ul
class="list list-unstyled"><li>You need to be physically strong to handle large jobs.</li><li>The cleaning market is very competitive.</li><li>Slow start to making a profit.</li></ul></div></div></div></div><div
