data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-irs-ein-application-288x288-20200624.png?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Get an Employer Identification Number (EIN)."></div></div><p>Every business is required to obtain an EIN if they plan on hiring employees. You can register for an EIN on the <a
href="https://www.irs.gov/businesses/small-businesses-self-employed/apply-for-an-employer-identification-number-ein-online">IRS website</a>.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-cleaning-business-section6-step4" class="step"><div
