</span><p>You can use your vehicle as an advertising tool for your cleaning business. You can put advertising on your vehicle, which enables you to promote your cleaning business as you go.</p></div></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-cleaning-business-section10" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>10.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=recruit-and-train-staff>Recruit and train staff.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-cleaning-business-section10-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>10.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=determine-your-ideal-candidate>Determine your ideal candidate.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-determine-your-ideal-candidate-288x288-20200729.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Determine your ideal candidate."></div></div><p>Your cleaning business is only as good as its employees. Therefore, your crew needs to be efficient, customer-focused, and able to deal with unique on-the-job challenges. To attract and recruit top talent, make use of an applicant tracking system that allows users to advertise jobs, gather resumes, and track applicants.</p><p><strong>Important skills to teach your employees include:</strong></p><ul><li>Client service.</li><li>Communication and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Time management.</li><li>Handling of cleaning equipment, detergents, and other chemicals.</li><li>Attention to detail and quality control skills.</li><li>Health and safety rules.</li><li>Compliance.</li></ul></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-cleaning-business-section11" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>11.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=market-your-cleaning-business>Market your cleaning business.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-cleaning-business-section11-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>11.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=offer-your-services-to-friends-and-family>Offer your services to friends and family.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-offer-services-to-family-and-friends-288x288-20200729.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Offer your services to friends and family."></div></div><p>This is a great way to get started and to spread the message about your cleaning business. Encourage your family and friends to tell people about your cleaning business and what you've got to offer.</p></div></div><div
