class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>11.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=use-free-marketing-options>Use free marketing options.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-use-free-marketing-platforms-288x288-20200730.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Use free marketing options."></div></div><p>There are free email and SMS marketing services available to help you cut your marketing expenses. You can also open a social media account for free on all popular platforms, including Facebook, LinkedIn, Twitter, and Instagram.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-cleaning-business-section11-step3" class="step"><div
